<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Thanks for Applying!</h1>

    <p>
    <%= @academy_application.first_name %>, your application has been recieved, you should hear from us within the next two days. Below is a confirmation of your application.
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>First name:</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.first_name %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Last name:</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.last_name %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>City:</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.city %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Country:</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.country %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Email:</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.email %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Phone:</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.phone %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Age:</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.age %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Gender:</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.gender %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Use one sentence to describe yourself:</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.one_line %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Please tell us why you are applying for this course:</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.reason %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>What is your background? Career, study, interests?</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.info %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>What is your passion in life?</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.passion %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Please describe what technology you have experience with, if any:</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.experience %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Write a couple of paragraphs about a time you faced a challenge in life and overcame it:</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.challenge %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Why should we choose you to be a student in this program?</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.special %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Relevant links:</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.links %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>How did you hear about this programme?</strong>
    <%= @academy_application.referral %>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
